  "subject": "Reduce onboarding wait intervals",
  "commit_message": "Reduce onboarding wait intervals\n\n- reduce onboarding check interval (45s -> 10s)\n- increase number of retries (30 -> 135)\n- this allows to finish earlier without changing the overall\n  maximum wait time (1350s)\n\nIssue-ID: INT-2369\nChange-Id: I82210d709143038f2ea4a5759923dd919e8cc7ec\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
